rows.label: bf01030100_0010
rows.name:
*sigh* We really do need to buy
ourselves a new depth probe...

rows.label: bf01030100_0020
rows.name:
The ping was off by 150 melts to
the east. That's not gonna fly!

rows.label: bf01030100_0030
rows.name:
And what about the treasure, Rex? Was
it in line with your expectations?

rows.label: bf01030100_0040
rows.name:
It seemed pretty solid. Didn't even
have to reinforce it too much.

rows.label: bf01030100_0050
rows.name:
Even with the labor costs, we should
be able to turn a decent profit.

rows.label: bf01030100_0060
rows.name:
Honestly, it takes you two days to
run the structural analysis...

rows.label: bf01030100_0070
rows.name:
Yet somehow you can gauge
the profits in an instant?

rows.label: bf01030100_0090
rows.name:
You know I'm in the salvaging
trade for the cash!

rows.label: bf01030100_0100
rows.name:
You could at least compliment
me on being capable!

rows.label: bf01030100_0120
rows.name:
I didn't expect THAT! You've been
living in this thing, big guy?

rows.label: bf01030100_0150
rows.name: I think we know what's for lunch!
